data.description: Don't miss out!  This 3 bedroom home conveniently located in the Cedar HIlls area has ALL NEW kitchen cabinets and quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances. Soft close cabinets, and high under Mount sink and sprayer in kitchen.  New beautiful laminate waterproof rugged floors through the entire home, carpet installed 2021 in gathering room, all new light fixtures, 200 amp electrical service, high efficiency toilet for water savings, and  new hvac installed 2022, updated plumbing, separate indoor laundry/storage/mud room off kitchen that could be divided for 2nd bathroom.   Living room accented with crown molding.  Additional space off living room for play room, etc. Large covered front porch. Large backyard with citrus tree fenced in back yard perfect for pets and families.  DON'T MISS OUT!!!
data.whatILove: Centrally located between Oak Leaf, Murray Hill, Orange Park and close to all major interstates which makes it super convenient for commutes and driving for entertainment.
